-- Toyota ADRs slide on sales suspension
-- 
-- Wed Jan 27, 2010 8:13am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2010/01/27/us-markets-stocks-beforethebell-toyota-idUSTRE60Q2UT20100127

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - New York-traded shares of Toyota Motor Co tumbled more than 6 percent before the opening bell on Wednesday after the Japanese carmaker told U.S. dealers to suspend sales of eight of its models, including the popular Camry. 

 The ADRs last traded down 6.1 percent at $81.45.